  <brief_title>Levetiracetam for Benign Rolandic Epilepsy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of Levetiracetam for Language Dysfunction Associated With Benign Epilepsy With Centrotemporal Spikes</official_title>
  <sponsors>
